title: S12 Ep229: Inside The Paranormal

description:
Why are we so interested in strange phenomena? Ghosts, UFOs, Cryptids. What is going on & why are we all so intrigued by the supernatural?

Dr. Brian D. Parsons weighs in on his research, his experiences and discusses the flaws & the wonder of investigating claims of the paranormal.
